            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-2648a2d0ac01f9ae-961711 twpub-2648a2d0ac01f9ae-c675eb twpub-2648a2d0ac01f9ae-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"footnote\"><a></a> <$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/2648a2d0ac01f9ae/text/000000026\">[1]</$link> Pronounced <i>Yoorghis</i></p></div></div>"
        },
